<h1>Locations</h1>
While the majority of the action unfolds in <b>Princeton Plainsboro Teaching Hospital</b> (PPTH), other locations are shown on screen, whether briefly (e.g. the patients' home), or regularly (Greg House's flat).
Here is a list of some of the locations shown in multiple episodes:

<dl>
  <dt>Princeton Plainsboro Teaching Hospital</dt>
  <dd>- Dean of Medicine's office</dd>
  <dd>- Diagnostics department</dd>
  <dd>- Oncology Department</dd>
  <dd>- Operating room</dd>
  <dd>- Emergency room</dd>
  <dd>- Morgue</dd>
  <dd>- Clinic duty</dd>
  <dd>- Pharmacy</dd>
  <dd>- Cafeteria</dd>
  <dd>- Coma ward</dd>
<br>
  <dt>Outside of PPTH</dt>
  <dd>- Geg House's flat (221B Baker Street)</dd>
  <dd>- James Wilson's hotel room</dd>
  <dd>- James Wilson and Greg House's condo</dd>
  <dd>- Amber Volakis' flat</dd>
</dl>
